# =============================================================================
# General-purpose .gitignore
# Covers: Python, Node/JS/TS, Go, Rust, Java, Kotlin, .NET/C#, C/C++,
#         Ruby, PHP, Docker, Terraform, editors (VS Code, JetBrains, Vim,
#         Emacs, Sublime), OS (macOS, Windows, Linux)
# Source: github.com/github/gitignore (CC0-1.0)
# =============================================================================


